These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, cooking, rock-climbing
3 different pets are kept: cat, fish, lizard
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, car, train
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the train##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
3. the person driving the car is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |   3   |
| Hobby        | rock-climbing | cooking | puzzles |
| Pet         | lizard    | cat     | fish  |
| Transport   | train     | car     | boat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, chess, woodworking
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, vegafina
1. the person who's hobby is chess is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person drinking fanta is between the vegafina-smoker and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |        3        |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta       | tea             |
| Hobby      | chess  | woodworking | card-games      |
| Cigar        | aristoff | baccarat    | vegafina |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, firefighter, mechanic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, spy
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, bike, bus
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the firefighter##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the car is between the mechanic and the person driving the bus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Job           | mechanic    | designer   | firefighter |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | disaster   | spy         |
| Transport         | bike     | car | bus     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, epic, romance
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, september, april
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, train
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the train is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person watching drama movies##2
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | epic  | drama     |
| Birthday   | february       | april   | september       |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, iced-tea
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, van
1. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person drinking cola is the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the frog and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | lemonade   | cola   |
| Pet           | frog   | ferret | rat     |
| Transport     | bike   | van    | jet-ski |

