1. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the musician is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's sport is baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Job   | teacher    | musician    | fisherman |
| Sport         | baseball   | tennis     | sailing     |
