.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-8::.
City: rome, colone, boston
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, indie, r&b
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, golf, surfing
1. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person traveling to rome is between the fan of indie and the person who's sport is climbing##2
4. the fan of indie is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| City         | boston | rome | colone  |
| Music-Genre   | indie        | r&b        | electronic |
| Sport         | golf         | surfing    | climbing   |

