.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-9::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, bartender, manager
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, turquise, amber
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, scooter, ship
1. the bartender is between the person who likes amber and the analyst##2
2. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the bike and the analyst##2
3. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Job         | manager | bartender  | analyst  |
| Color         | amber    | green | turquise |
| Transport   | bike    | ship       | scooter  |

