.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-2-11::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, trike, van
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, jazz, rock
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding, skiing
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is between the person driving the van and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |       3       |
| Transport         | van | roller  | trike |
| Music-Genre   | jazz      | hip-hop       | rock          |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | skateboarding | skiing        |

