1. the person watching family movies is the fan of country##1
2. the engineer is on the far left##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the nurse is between the fan of gospel and the fan of country##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery | animation | family |
| Job           | engineer   | nurse   | bartender |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | ambient | country   |

